column5: http://www.bushparty.com/htms/twas2.htm  Thought some of you would enjoy this.

Thanks for sharing!  Here's a sorta funny fishing picture I found surfing on Stumble-upon. Stumble-upon's an add on for your internet browser that lets you check off your interests, then you just click the stumble button and it brings you to a random site based on your interests. I find all sorts of funny fishing stuff on there, not usually worth a whole topic on OFC but still funny....maybe we should have a thread for funny fishing internet stuff? just an idea, I'm always finding cool stuff when I'm in class....I mean at home  .  -Ben
Good old Red fisher ... the godfather of fishing shows ... yep ...I remember waiting for Saturday monrings to watch Scuttlebut lodge
with a few name changes in the poem I could make it apply to our group in the spring.  Thanks for finding it and sharing
